M||tx|When the us wants to cr or op an em sequence, drip cg, automated em flow, or lifecycle em program. Also use when the us mentions "em sequence," "drip cg," "nurture sequence," "onboarding emails," "welcome sequence," "re-engagement emails," "em automation," "lifecycle emails," "trigger-based emails," "em funnel," "em workflow," "what emails shd I send," "welcome series," or "em cadence." Use this for any multi-em automated flow. For cold outreach emails, see cold-em. For in-app onboarding, see onboarding-cro.
